publisher			Geek Sloth Games							
publish_time	 2015年2月9日		
desc_long							评测						“With games like Nidhogg, Samurai Gunn, and TowerFall, we live in a golden age of same-screen 2D melee arena murderfun. Let’s keep an eye on Samudai then.”Rock, Paper, Shotgun“Do you enjoy fighting games? How about cute kittens? If the answer to both of these questions is “yes” then please direct your attention to Samudai.”Cliqist“In the vein of recent games like Nidhogg and Samurai Gunn, stylish yet simplistic Samudai aims for arena brawling excellence.”Indie Love													特色列表									Seven Challenging StagesFrom Waterfalls to Bamboo Forests and Icy Peaks… where will your power take you? Each stage has unique mechanics that could change to outcome of battle. Push forward and fight against your friends and the environment itself!For the ultimate party fighter there are 5 different modes to choose from!Main ModeStand your ground against your friends and push them to their limit! Slash, dash and claw your way to victory defeating them throughout Mount Samudai and face off against their Ultimate Boss Mode! Yarn BallTired of fighting and need some relaxation? Try a round of Yarn Ball! Use all the skills at your disposal to take control of the Yarn Ball and score goals, alone or in a team.Emperor of the HillTake control of the Emperor’s hat and prevent others from taking it until the time runs out.Hold you GroundDefend the highlighted area from other players. Each second in the area reduces your timer, first one to zero wins!Last Cat StandingUse all you have learnt to fight your friends until there is only one Samudai standing!Full Controller SupportControl the whole game from the couch in Big Picture mode!Original SoundtrackFantastic oriental beats by composer Barry Pietersen bring a unique sound to Samudai and all it’s modes.AchievementsUnlock challenging achievements that will test your skills across all modes of Samudai.																						关于这款游戏							Samudai is a local multiplayer party fighter with Samurai Cats, lightning fast action, and multiple hazardous stages.Stand your ground against your friends and push them to their limit! Slash, dash and claw your way to victory defeating them throughout Mount Samudai and face off against their Ultimate Boss Mode!Take up to four friends and engage in multiple extra modes in teams or free for all and decide once and for all who the true Samudai is!						
